{"code":"from pydub import AudioSegment
import speech_recognition as sr

# Load the audio file
audio = AudioSegment.from_mp3('2b3ef98c-cc05-450b-a719-711aee40ac65.mp3')

# Export to a format that can be processed by speech recognition
audio.export('converted.wav', format='wav')

# Initialize recognizer
recognizer = sr.Recognizer()

# Load the audio file for recognition
with sr.AudioFile('converted.wav') as source:
    audio_data = recognizer.record(source)
    
# Recognize the speech in the audio
text = recognizer.recognize_google(audio_data)

text","packages":["pydub","speechrecognition"]}
